window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Join the world's most famous drow elf in the penultimate chapter of the <i>Legend of Drizzt</i> series! Spending time in the unimaginable torture chambers of the Abyss for even a day would be enough to break even the heartiest soul, and the barbarian Wulfgar was there for years. When he returns, his friends find him a changed man, and not changed for the better. But Wulfgar's road to redemption is one he must travel on his own, even if it leads to the bottle. </p>"; 
